title: Mulling Mueller (with Anne Milgram)
description:
Anne Milgram, the former Attorney General of New Jersey, returns to help answer your questions about the Mueller investigation. Will anyone else be indicted? How long is this going to take? And did Jeff Sessions really try to find 'dirt' on James Comey?
Do you have a question for Preet? Tweet them to @PreetBharara or call 669-247-7338 and leave a voicemail.
